## Notes
- Video thumbnails are generated as PNG files in the same directory as the source video
- PDF table extraction supports different strategies for better accuracy
- PDF table detection sensitivity can be controlled with threshold parameters:
  - `snap=N` - Controls how close lines must be to be considered part of the same table
  - `edge=N` - Controls how close edges must be to be considered part of the same table
  - `intersect=N` - Controls how close edges must be to be considered intersecting
- All file paths are relative to the .dmd file location
